metadata.title: Ciliary Protein Interaction Network - Complete Dataset
metadata.description: AlphaFold3 predicted interactions for IFT and BBSome proteins

scoring_method.primary_metric: ipSAE (interface Predicted Aligned Error Structure-based Average Estimate)

confidence_classification.high: ipSAE > 0.7 (strong evidence, virtually no false positives)

column_descriptions.ipsae: ipSAE score (0-1 scale, higher = stronger interaction confidence)
column_descriptions.ipsae_confidence_class: Confidence classification based on ipSAE score
column_descriptions.mean_interface_plddt: Mean per-residue confidence score for interface residues
column_descriptions.contacts_pae_lt_3: Number of residue pairs with PAE < 3Å and Cβ-Cβ ≤ 8Å
column_descriptions.contacts_pae_lt_6: Number of residue pairs with PAE < 6Å and Cβ-Cβ ≤ 8Å
column_descriptions.source_path: Path to original AlphaFold3 prediction directory
column_descriptions.quality_class: Original quality classification from v3 analysis
